channel.title: Comments on: Stila Stay All Day Waterproof Liquid Eyeliner

item.title: By: Sarah Cosper
item.dc:creator: Sarah Cosper
item.description:
In reply to <a href="/stila-stay-all-day-waterproof-liquid-eyeliner/#comment-342">Suzi</a>.
Ummm. Wow. I just watched this, and I'm impressed! I saw what she was going to to do to lay that first line down, and I said out loud, "Ahhhhhhhh. Clever." I'm really glad you found something that works for you. Just keep practicing, and soon, you won't even need to line it up, your eye and hand will just know where to stop. Well, most of the time anyways. Like, 95% of the time.

item.title: By: Suzi
item.dc:creator: Suzi
item.description:
Okay, so I withheld allowing myself to comment on this one until I could finally give myself an acceptable cat eye. I'm so jealous of your skills. About a billion Youtube tutorials later, I finally got it! This is the one that finally worked for me: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DLLNohnjRJU
It's like magic. And they match each other! As a reward, I'm letting myself get this Stila liner.
